name: Beautiful Asian Pop Star Yang Chaoyue 杨超越
description:
Trained on 16 images, mostly close-up portrait of Chinese actress/pop singer 杨超越 Yang Chaoyue. Processed with focal point crop. Weight this embedding at 0.8~1.2 is suggested. See sample images and png info to grab some prompts that just works.

Hires.fix on is suggested (e.g. 512*768--2x-->1024*1536, Hires steps 18,Denoising strength 0.15, ESRGAN_4x or LDSR are highly suggested as always, depending on trade-off between speed and super-sharp details.)

Try out Restore Faces when generating side view photos since the training set isn't varied enough concerning poses and angle, though it performs quite well on contrapposto or selfie photos.

中文翻译 Simplified Chinese Translation:

训练了 16 张图像，大部分是中国女演员/流行歌手 杨超越的特写肖像。使用焦点裁剪处理。建议将此嵌入权重设置为 0.8~1.2。查看示例图像和 png 信息以获取一些有效的提示。

建议启用 Hires.fix超分辨率（例如 512*768--2x-->1024*1536，Hires 步骤 18，去噪强度 0.15，一如既往地强烈建议 ESRGAN_4x 或 LDSR，取决于你在速度和细节之间的权衡)

在生成侧视图照片时尝试 Restore Faces，因为训练集在姿势和角度方面的变化不够大，尽管它在 contrapposto 或自拍照片上表现相当不错。

请勿用于商业用途或生成违法/侵权照片用于传播。
